<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dhurandhar Art & Gallery</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #faf9f6; /* Off-white canvas feel */
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header & Navigation */
        header {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo-area {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo-placeholder {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #aec6cf, #b19cd9);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo-text h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Hero / Profile Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: #f0f4f8;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            background: #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 60px;
        }

        /* Gallery Section */
        .gallery-container {
            padding: 50px;
        }

        .gallery-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .art-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .art-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .art-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            background: #e9e9e9;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #aaa;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .art-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .art-info h3 {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .art-info p {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo-area">
            <div class="logo-placeholder">🎨</div>
            <div class="logo-text">
                <h1>Dhurandhar</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="avatar">👓</div>
        <h2>The Artist & Detective</h2>
        <p>Mastering Water-color Sakuntala, Geometry Solvers, & Solving Mysteries.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="gallery-container">
        <h2 class="gallery-title">The Masterpieces</h2>
        
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="art-card">
                <div class="art-img">
                    Water-color Sakuntala Image Placeholder
                </div>
                <div class="art-info">
                    <h3>Water-color Sakuntala</h3>
                    <p>A fluid, traditional blend of strokes bringing classic poetry to life.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="art-card">
                <div class="art-img">
                    Geometry Art Placeholder
                </div>
                <div class="art-info">
                    <h3>Geometric Cube Nets</h3>
                    <p>Where precise mathematical structure meets abstract aesthetics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="art-card">
                <div class="art-img">
                    Byomkesh Tribute Placeholder
                </div>
                <div class="art-info">
                    <h3>Chapa Khanar Khun</h3>
                    <p>A dark, noir-style visual tribute to classic detective mysteries.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Dhurandhar Art. Created by Rocky (Your PBF) 🚀</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
